 ('350', '384', 'en_us', 'Founders Day', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>On the firstSundayin October 1848, George Hendric Houghton gathered a band of twenty-four followers for a celebration of Holy Communion in the parlor of the home of the Rev. Dr. Lawson Carter, an elderly priest, on East 24th Street. None of those first worshipers could have imagined that they had just attended the first service of the Church of the Transfiguration, later to be celebrated as The Little Church Around the Corner. The twenty-eight year-old priest who called this small congregation into being, however, had a clear vision in mind: to establish a parish that would minister to the poor and needy of New York City. The first service in the new church was held on Sunday, March 28th, 1850. <em>(excerpted from A Parish Guide to The Church of the Transfiguration by Zulette M. Catir)</em>  </p>\n<p>His motto was<em>Fides Opera</em>(Faith and Works)\n</p>', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', 'Portrait of Dr. Houghton by Ralph L. Boyer', NULL, '2017-09-16 21:50:54', '2017-10-06 13:09:44', '2fe11b9b-78b6-48c0-990b-4a04a1af117a'),
 ('353', '387', 'en_us', 'Blessing of the Animals', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Thanks to all members and visitors who came out on Sunday, October 8th for Blessing of the Pets. Stay tuned as more pictures are posted later this week.</p>', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, '2017-09-16 22:31:41', '2017-10-09 12:15:13', '74a69c4b-63d7-4f44-8cda-6fc8f3f5eaae'),
 ('354', '388', 'en_us', 'Open House New York', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jesse Anders/On Point Images', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Come explore \"The Little Church Around the Corner\"at your leisure with a self-guided tour or enjoy one of our special presentations listed below.</p>\n<p><br /><strong>Saturday</strong><br />10:30 am: Guided Tour: History, Art, &amp;Architecture of the Little Church<br />11:30 am: Concert:Wedding Favorites<br /><em>         featuring the Boys\' and Girls\' Choir of the Church of the Transfiguration<br /></em>12:00 pm:Talk and Tour:Marriage at the Little Church<br /><em>        with</em><em>Fr. John David van Dooren, Rector</em><br /><em></em>1:00 pm: Guided Tour:History, Art, &amp; Architecture of the Little Church<br />1:00 pm: Visita con Guia: La Historia, el Arte, y la Arquitectura de la Pequea Iglesia<br /> 2:00 pm: Concert showcasing the Arnold Schwartz Memorial Organ<br /><em>        featuring</em><em>Dr. Claudia Dumschat, Organist<br /></em> 3:00 pm: Guided Tour: History, Art, &amp;Architecture of the Little Church</p>\n<p><strong>Sunday</strong><br />11:00 am: Solemn High Mass <em>with Choir</em><br />12:45 pm: Children\'s Guided Tour: Birds, Beasts, and Bees of The Little Church<br /> 1:00 pm: Guided Tour:History, Art, &amp; Architecture of the Little Church<br /> 2:00pm: \"A Celebration of Song\" Hits from Broadway and Beyond <br /><em>          with</em><em>Members of the Episcopal Actors Guild</em><br /> 2:30 pm: Guided Tour:History, Art, &amp; Architecture of the Little Church</p>\n<p><strong>Historic church vestments will be on display throughout the weekend.</strong></p>\n<p><br /></p>', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'http://onpointimages.com', '', NULL, '2017-09-16 22:37:49', '2017-10-04 19:49:00', 'a973c6bd-c811-423e-a2ad-f02ab265088f'),
