 ('483', '532', 'en_us', 'Plan Your Visit', '<p>We love to have visitors. Every Sunday sees a stream of visitors who come here to photograph the stained-glass windows, wander through the nooks and crannies, and discover the unexpected, such as the actor Rex Harrisons memorial plaque placed next to a Madonna window. Some come for a guided tour and listen to the story of how we came to be called the \"Little Church Around the Corner.\" Others come to carry out research on our various art and artifacts.<br /></p>\n<h2>Hours of Operation</h2>\n<p> The main church is open Sundays from 8:10 am to 5:00 pm (or the close of Evening Mass) and on special occasions as advertised.</p>\n<p>In addition, the Holy Family Chapel is open on most Monday evenings from 6:00 pm to 6:45 pm when the Meditation Group meets, and also on most Thursdays evenings for 6:30 pm Mass when the Bible Study Group is meeting.\n					</p>\n<p>The Parish Office is open Monday through Friday from  9:00 am to 5:00 pm.</p>\n<h3>Guided Tours</h3>\n<p>Guided tours are available every Sunday morning at 12:45 pm. Meet at the organ in the Main Church. Group tours are available by appointment.</p>\n<p><em>To contact the Parish Office or book a tour, call 212 684-6770 or e-mail  <a href=\"mailto:receptionist@littlechurch.org\">receptionist@littlechurch.org.</a></em></p>', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jesse Anders/On Point Images', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, 'Getting Here', 'Take the 1, R/W, or 6 to 28th Street, or take the B/D/F/M/N/Q to Herald Square.', 'M1, M2, M3, M5, M6, M7.', 'http://onpointimages.com', '', NULL, '2017-09-27 07:44:52', '2017-10-03 23:13:38', '38d8875b-6b3d-4836-801d-5bd25f99e3bd'),
 ('485', '534', 'en_us', 'Concert Series', '<p>Fallconcert: Rule Britannia<br />$15: buy tickets at door</p>\n<p>Music by Arne, Purcell, Hume, Butler, Simpson, Locke and Morley<br />Founded in 1994. Empire Viols has focused on the rich repertoire for two viols<br />and harpsichord, while expanding its programs through daring and adventurous<br />transcriptions. The ensemble (Martha McGaughey and Carlene Stober, viols;<br />Arthur Haas, harpsichord) performs in the Northeast U.S. and beyond, and was<br />featured on composer Debra Kayes debut CD, And So It Begins, on RavelloRecords.</p>', NULL, NULL, '/music/concert-series', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, '<p>Music by Arne, Purcell, Hume, Butler, Simpson, Locke, and Morley. Founded in 1994, Empire Viols has focused on the rich repertoire for two violsand harpsichord, while expanding its programs through daring and adventurous transcriptions. The ensemble (Martha McGaughey and Carlene Stober, viols;Arthur Haas, harpsichord) performs in the Northeast U.S. and beyond, and wasfeatured on composer Debra Kayes debut CD, And So It Begins, on RavelloRecords.<br /></p>', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Fall&nbsp;Concert: Rule Britannia<br>Empire Viols<br><em>$15:&nbsp;<em>buy tickets at door</em></em></p>', '2017-09-27 10:30:52', '2017-10-03 23:38:20', 'e0f83125-8afa-4d99-96d6-187bd86e8f03'),
 ('487', '536', 'en_us', 'Concert Series', NULL, NULL, NULL, '/music/concert-series', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Featuring a musical offering of Bachs Cantata 106<em>Gottes Zeit ist der beste Zeit (Gods Time is the Best Time).</em>Marie Marquis, Christian Kay, sopranos: Joe Redd, alto; Ben Thomas, tenor; Jake Ingbar, baritone. The Transfiguration Period Instrument Ensemble and Camerata, Claudia Dumschat, conductor.</p>', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>A Mass For All Souls Day<br><em>Free admission</em></p>', '2017-09-27 10:51:11', '2017-10-01 11:16:22', '4d795e90-d10c-4c4a-823b-905bdb5cfbcf'),
 ('488', '537', 'en_us', 'Concert Series', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Colombian-born guitarist Francisco Roldn performed, in the past year, in Portugal, Greece and at the Mannes Guitar Festival in New York, among otherconcerts. This year hes performed at the Mid Hudson Classical Guitar Society and at Symphony Space in NY. Mr. Roldn has performed in Russia, Argentina, Spain, Colombia, the Dominican Republic, Paraguay and throughout the United States.</p>', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>A Celebration of Latin American Cultural Week<br>Francisco Roldn, guitar<br><em>$15: buy tickets at door</em></p>', '2017-09-27 10:59:50', '2017-10-01 11:16:39', '4387eb5e-2f26-4f90-b7a1-b7be2475f0b8'),
