 ('85', '69', '7', '1', 'en_us', '38', '', '{\"typeId\":\"7\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Welcome\",\"slug\":\"welcome\",\"postDate\":1503746520,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":\"Welcome to our little church\",\"13\":{\"71\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<h2>First time here?<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>I invite you to join us in worship and fellowship at any one of our services, coffee hour, concert series, or a simple contemplative visit to our garden and chapel. I like to think of our parish as a quiet oasis in the heart of this vibrant city. And yet we have so much going on at our Little Church.<\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":[\"207\"],\"12\":\"<p>Greetings and welcome to the Church of the Transfiguration, also known affectionately as the \\u201cLittle Church Around the Corner\\u201d.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Our parish combines the beauty and depth of the Anglo-Catholic tradition with the warmth of a dear community of people seeking the presence of Christ in the center of the NoMad neighborhood in Manhattan.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>From the time of our founding in the mid 19th century, our motto has remained Fides Opera (Faith & Works).&nbsp; Our faith is expressed in the depth of resplendent worship, offering our very best in praise of God in the person of Jesus Christ.&nbsp; And from this worship flows an outward ministry of works to a city and world crying for mindful and responsive hands, feet, and hearts. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u201cIn God, that which is ancient never becomes old,\\u201d and we embrace this sentiment combining traditional liturgical worship with a radical inclusiveness deeply rooted in our parish\\u2019s history and celebrated by a vibrant diocese in which we serve.&nbsp; Please consider this parish as you look for a spiritual home.&nbsp; All are welcome.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>With loving wishes,&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fr. John David van Dooren<br>Rector<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\",\"27\":\"Meghan Joseph\"}}', '2017-08-31 12:09:11', '2017-08-31 12:09:11', '1fc26a65-38d5-4ea9-9564-50a5a12528bc'),
