d gives them to artists in need who have applied to the Guild for help. No one leaves empty-handed.<\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":\"\",\"12\":\"\",\"27\":\"\"}}', '2017-09-06 16:30:07', '2017-09-06 16:30:07', 'ab407756-0944-4194-a6ee-36bbbaadce1a'),
